channel.title: Davidson Ospina / Ospina Digital Podcast
channel.description: Why do you want to listen to Ospina’s podcast? Is it because he throws down hard-boiled, dirty soul funk and booty shakin’ rubber disco? Yes, yes it is. But, don’t take our word for it. Click on the damn link and hear for yourself! Disclaimer: Oh, and you will want to go out to the club tonight after this. The music and any side effects are not representative of us, therein. Any need for clubbing is the sole responsibility of the listener. We warned you.
